'''''Aardvark''''' is a maze video game for the [[Commodore 64]], and [[Commodore 16]] published by [[Bug-Byte]] in 1986. ''Aardvark'' is based on 1982 arcade game ''[[Anteater (video game)|Anteater]]'' and 1983 [[Atari 8-bit computers|Atari 8-bit computer]] game ''Ardy The Aardwark'' designed by [[Christian Oberth|Chris Oberth]].

==Gameplay==
The player must collect [[ant]] [[larva]] using the snout of an [[aardvark]].

